<author>hạny ạ̉nys, qs ạ̉mjd sʿd</author>
<title>tsbyḥ yʿlạlk wyzyd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (tsbyḥ yʿlạ lk wyzyd .. wnfws ttḥdy̱ ạlạ̉tʿạb
 bạ̹ymạn ttḥqq mwạʿyd .. wmlknạ dạ rb ạlạ̉rbạb)2
 1- (wsṭ ạlạ̉zmạt .. wʿdk mḍmwn
 mn byn ậlạmạt .. trfʿ wtṣwn)2
 2- (ạ̉ʿly̱ ạlạ̉swạr .. bndws ʿạbryn
 wlạ ywm nḥtạr .. wyạk gẖạlbyn)2
 3- (nksr ạ̉rwạḥ .. nfrḥ wyạk
 wqlwb trtạḥ .. ysbyhạ gẖnạk)2
 4- (wạ̉rạḍy bʿyd .. ạlywm hạtʿwd
 bạlwʿd ạ̉kyd .. hạnfk qywd)2
 5- (ạ̉frạḥ wsẖfạʾ .. gẖfrạn bạ̹ymạn
 wyạk yạ rjạʾ .. kl ạlạ̉zmạn)2</lyrics>
</song>